 * IPL Sunflare - Hero Slider Component
 *
 * @component_start
 * code: hero-slider
 * name: Hero首屏
 * name_en: Hero Slider
 * description: 暖色动感首屏，强调速度感与信息扫描效率
 * category: content
 * region: content
 * @component_end
 *
 * @fields_start
 *
 * group:display => 显示控制
 * hero.display => 显示首屏模块:select:yes|yes,no
 *
 * group:hero => Hero设置
 * hero.title => 主标题:text:Play Faster in the IPL Sunflare Arena
 * hero.kicker => 顶部提示:text:IPL Inspired Heatwave Design
 * hero.subtitle => 副标题:textarea:A warm, motion-driven landing experience built for quick sessions, clear action points, and mobile-first readability.
