 * hero.cta_text => CTA按钮文字:text:Start Match
 * hero.cta_url => CTA按钮链接:text:#download
 * hero.secondary_cta_text => 次按钮文字:text:Explore Modes
 * hero.secondary_cta_url => 次按钮链接:text:#modes
 * hero.image => 左侧图片:textarea:|留空使用默认图
 * hero.image_mobile => 移动端主视觉:textarea:|留空跟随桌面图
 * hero.bg_color => 背景基础色:color:#150912
 * hero.bg_image => 背景图片:textarea:|留空使用默认图
 *
 * group:download_btn => 下载资源
 * download_btn.display => 显示下载资源:select:no|yes,no
 * download_btn.image => 下载按钮图片:textarea:
 * download_btn.alt => 下载按钮描述:text:Join Live Table
 * download_btn.url => 下载按钮链接:text:#download
 *
 * group:layout => 布局设置
 * layout.slider_classes => 区域CSS类:textarea:isf-hero
 * layout.margin_top => 区域顶部偏移:number:0|px
 * layout.img_margin_top => 图片顶部偏移:number:0|px

 * group:stage => 舞台文案
 * stage.badge => 舞台标签:text:Feature Spotlight
 * stage.ticker_items => 顶部滚动标签:textarea:Live Heat\nQuick Join\nTouch Ready\nUltra Responsive\nWarm Palette\nModular Config
 * stage.signal_1_value => 信号1数值:text:10s
 * stage.signal_1_label => 信号1标签:text:Average turn
 * stage.signal_2_value => 信号2数值:text:24/7
 * stage.signal_2_label => 信号2标签:text:Live activity
 * stage.signal_3_value => 信号3数值:text:1 Tap
 * stage.signal_3_label => 信号3标签:text:Room entry
 * stage.track_1_label => 轨道1标题:text:Fast Queue
 * stage.track_1_value => 轨道1描述:textarea:Mode selection stays one glance away
 * stage.track_2_label => 轨道2标题:text:Readable UI
 * stage.track_2_value => 轨道2描述:textarea:Cards and actions stay clear on small screens
 * stage.track_3_label => 轨道3标题:text:High Rhythm
 * stage.track_3_value => 轨道3描述:textarea:Layouts are tuned for back-to-back sessions
 *
 * @fields_end
